								<h1 class="page-title">Contacting My Child’s School During the COVID-19/Coronavirus Closure</h1>

								

								<div class="at-above-post-page addthis_tool" data-url="https://www.sgfcsd.org/contacting-my-childs-school-during-the-covid-19-coronavirus-closure/"></div>
<p>While classes are canceled amidst the COVID-19/Coronavirus, here is how to get in touch with your child’s school.</p>
<h3>District Office</h3>
